Ordering of adjectives

When we can use more than one adjective together to describe something or someone. 
The adjectives follow a certain order.

1 - opinion
beautiful
delicious
nice
pretty
ugly

2 - size
big
small
large
tall
short

3 - age
old
young 
modern
fresh

4 - color
red
blue
yellow
black

5 - origin
French
Chinese
British
Thai
Italian

6 - material
cotton
silver
wool
silk
nylon

beautiful old chinese table

ugly red cotton dress

delicious fresh italian dish
